{"tid":1487379,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買島資訊匯總","createTime":"2019-08-19T08:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:23:19.000Z","uid":295524,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"7326fe73225a3b4a8a98f1e751e90b00a8671007","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"買島件事，依家唔係好多人關注概焦點。我只係把目前看到的資訊整理下，以備不時之需。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於之前好多巴打講福克蘭太凍，地理位置遠離大陸、遠離發達國家⋯⋯我都找尋左其他一些選擇。因為呢個係為左萬一的方舟計劃，唔係為左私人地產發展或者私人度假庄園，所以我概篩選條件依次係：面積&mdash;氣候&mdash;地區。<br />\n<br />\n目前全球可供出售的最大島嶼係智利太平洋海岸線上，面積10萬acres=大約404平方公里，與香港目前的開發面積差唔多。無人島，有淡水資源，緯度大約等於北半球的日本北海道，比福克蘭群島暖。<br />\n<br />\n其他另有加拿大湖區、美國東海岸的一些島，最大的面積在5000acres左右。若干好友買來開發有的諗，作方舟基本唔可能。<br />\n<br />\n有巴打講希臘正在賣島，的確如此，佢賣嘅最大島嶼面積僅僅1350acres，但已經係目前全歐洲for sale的最大島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n印尼與巴拿馬也有兩個面積稍大的島，供參考。<br />\n<br />\n無法預測isle of man概可能性，但係同樣在以下的圖中列出。<br />\n<br />\n希望多D人討論。我自己覺得期望住美國澳洲等發達國家割飛地比香港人基本是白日夢。英國屬地比其他發達國家可能性大小小，但亦未知。人工島就屬於太過長遠概打算，如果唔係政府資金投入，私人資本在咁長時間無可觀收益，機會成本太高，無知邊個LP會投資。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔可能搵到方舟，基本上香港人只能做好作順民、在動盪環境下係香港長期堅持，或者大家各謀出路四散移民解體香港社會，呢三種準備。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JO9rghM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJO9rghM.png&h=6886d91c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oh3GPCN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOh3GPCN.png&h=9526773f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnH05a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnH05a8.png&h=a21a4837&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALSwspu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALSwspu.png&h=46332f27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5mX7pw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5mX7pw.png&h=6fd06066&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaNz9CS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaNz9CS.png&h=2fb20fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuxgDwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuxgDwd.png&h=8de26c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2UKNpz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2UKNpz.png&h=089dc0cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuaYRRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuaYRRf.png&h=71469a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkzVT4B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkzVT4B.png&h=6fe0ad5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"457d75824def25d0baa5e554f9770acb241f7616","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b222fccae8a9de6712691919cd342cf25e3065e","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89e0c2bfdfe403b794a355639b85bc6079098314","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e452867304459a705e68f1f17f3c36248abb4704","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bef624dc8d088300c8bcc7550e8e15dcf1271c43","tid":1487379,"uid":295524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae50d2c8d4775679df29fc57fece2631fdaa5dfc","tid":1487379,"uid":24517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"多謝你分享<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da30987500cea47b4ebf7b677cdb32acd9ac440f","tid":1487379,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ado